# Tests skipped by run_link_testsuite only (one per line; # comments, blank
# lines ignored; same entry format as the shared blacklist). The shared
# blacklist still applies too; this file is for tests a static merge linker
# structurally cannot run, so they are not linker bugs.

# These files' only linking content imports a memory / table that the spec
# grows at instantiation *before* the importing module is instantiated, so the
# import's declared minimum exceeds the exporter's declared minimum. A static
# merge linker checks the declared limits and rightly rejects it — it cannot
# observe the runtime growth. (Files with other, linkable, import tests are
# kept; only wholly-runtime-growth files are skipped here.)
memory_grow.wast
table_grow.wast
